textAfterTable: When your regular season is 162 games, you have to be ready for anything. That includes unpredictable conditions. New York Mets third baseman David Wright knows the right apparel can help level the playing field physically, and give you a mental edge. He is proof that not all ball players are created equal. The same holds true for apparel. So if a piece of apparel is going to make it into David's rotation, it has to perform at the highest level. He would know something about it.
